{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.360", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.840", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.720", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mali ist der gef\u00e4hrlichste Einsatz der Bundeswehr. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.280", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Um ihn einzusch\u00e4tzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.960", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "lohnt sich ein Blick nach Afghanistan, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.160", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wo nach 17\u00a0Jahren des Einsatzes die Taliban an den Verhandlungstisch gebeten werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.320", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sind so m\u00e4chtig wie seit ihrem Sturz 2001 nicht mehr. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.000", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man beginnt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.280", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "einzusehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.440", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass hier der Krieg verloren ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.880", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "57\u00a0Bundeswehrsoldaten lie\u00dfen ihr Leben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.920", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Anzahl der PTBS-Betroffenen und geschiedenen Ehen werden wir nie erfahren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.440", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dass die Regierung unsere Soldaten vor diesem Hintergrund erneut in einen Einsatz mit diffusen Missionszielen schicken will, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.000", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist verantwortungslos. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.400", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sollten es inzwischen besser wissen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.080", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein Blick in Ihren Antrag zeigt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.480", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie k\u00f6nnen gar nicht klar erkl\u00e4ren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.120", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wof\u00fcr unsere Soldaten ihr Leben riskieren sollen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.680", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schutz von Zivilpersonen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.440", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Anbieten guter Dienste, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.240", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erhalt malischen Kulturgutes usw. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.440", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das steht in Ihrem Antrag. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.360", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich frage mich: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.600", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wann sind denn solche Ziele eigentlich erf\u00fcllt? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.640", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine internationale Milit\u00e4roperation, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.960", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in deren Rahmen wir mit Widerstand durch gut organisierte irregul\u00e4re Kr\u00e4fte rechnen m\u00fcssen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.240", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "braucht klare Ziele und Meilensteine. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.320", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundesregierung kann von verantwortungsvollen Bundestagsabgeordneten nicht erwarten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.560", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie unsere Soldaten in eine solche Mission schicken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.840", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um dann abzuwarten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.600", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was passiert."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.720", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieser Einsatz bringt alle Voraussetzungen mit sich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.000", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der n\u00e4chste Endloseinsatz der Bundeswehr zu werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.680", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Werte Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.560", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es tut mir leid, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.760", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihnen das sagen zu m\u00fcssen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.520", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber den Soldaten interessiert in der Hauptsache gar nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.000", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie ausgiebig er hier von Ihnen immer gelobt wird; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.320", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ihn interessiert vielmehr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "127.680", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gesund zu bleiben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "127.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.440", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00fcber eine gute Ausr\u00fcstung zu verf\u00fcgen und nicht in sinnlose Eins\u00e4tze entsandt zu werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.160", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die ihn von seiner Familie wegholen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.800", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unsere Soldaten haben auch im Vertrauen auf dieses Parlament geschworen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.960", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das eigene Leben einzusetzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "149.840", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn es sein muss. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "149.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.960", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir tragen hier eine hohe Verantwortung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.440", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich denke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.920", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir sind uns alle einig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.480", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass unsere Soldaten mehr sind als ein zahlenm\u00e4\u00dfiges au\u00dfenpolitisches Statement. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.400", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir reden hier \u00fcber V\u00e4ter, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.080", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "M\u00fctter, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.520", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "S\u00f6hne und T\u00f6chter. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.040", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn man sie in den Kampf schickt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.480", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann erwarte ich ein klares Konzept und ein nationales Interesse, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.240", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber keine Phrasen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.280", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie schreiben in Ihrem eigenen Antrag, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.160", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sich die Lage in Mali verschlechtert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.440", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Radikale Islamisten k\u00f6nnen in mehreren afrikanischen Staaten relativ ungest\u00f6rt agieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.520", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Weder k\u00f6nnen wir sie in ihren R\u00fcckzugsgebieten bek\u00e4mpfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.760", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "noch k\u00f6nnen wir ihre Ideologie besiegen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.560", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und selbst wenn es anders w\u00e4re: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.440", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt keinen guten Grund daf\u00fcr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.920", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass ein deutsches Kind in Mali seinen Vater verliert."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.840", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der fundamentalistische Islam wird in Afrika \u00fcbrigens besonders von Saudi-Arabien verbreitet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.560", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auf der einen Seite st\u00e4rken Sie diesen Staat mit deutschen R\u00fcstungsg\u00fctern; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.800", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auf der anderen Seite sollen deutsche Soldaten ihr Leben riskieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.560", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um den Schaden einzud\u00e4mmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.560", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den sie in Afrika anrichten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.680", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das nennt man Doppelmoral."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.360", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir k\u00f6nnen weiter in Ihrem Antrag lesen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.360", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass alte Konflikte in Mali neu aufflammen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.640", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mali ist ein sehr armes Land mit einem Altersdurchschnitt von 17. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "250.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.720", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wo viele junge Menschen ohne Perspektive leben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.680", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da kommt es zu Konflikten; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.320", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber daran kann auch die Bundeswehr nichts \u00e4ndern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.040", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Lage in Mali h\u00e4ngt nicht an dieser oder jener Terrorgruppe; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "265.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.440", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Realit\u00e4t ist weitaus komplexer."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "268.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.280", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hier fehlt ein Konzept; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "270.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "272.400", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hier fehlt das nationale Interesse. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "272.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "274.320", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer diesem Einsatz zustimmt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "274.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "277.400", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der hat aus Afghanistan nichts gelernt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "277.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "278.760", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir lehnen ihn ab. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "278.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "282.000", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da wir f\u00fcr eine konsequente R\u00fcckf\u00fchrung von Migranten stehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "282.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "288.080", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "lehnen wir den Entschlie\u00dfungsantrag der Linken ebenfalls ab."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "288.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "294.640", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Danke."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "294.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "297.720", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "N\u00e4chster Redner ist Paul Ziemiak f\u00fcr die CDU/CSU."
   ]
  }
 ]
}